\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

stationary
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

/
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

frozen
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 burst).
 During such read, each word must be read by 32-bit access (
\series bold
\shape italic
sbe
\series default
\shape default
=
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

1111
\begin_inset Quotes erd
