 Stuff Pipeline stage is also shifted by one clock cycle (from last clock
 cycle of TSEG2 to first clock cycle of TSEG1).
 As value of Information Processing Time of CTU CAN FD is 2, this situation
 corresponds to shortening length of TSEG2 to less than Information Processing
 Time.
 Throttling of TX Trigger corresponds to delaying calculation of following
 bit value after Information Processing Time from Sample Point as defined
 in 11.3.2.4 of 
